nd your position, your pressures, and what a strong outcome looks like for you.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"service-type_header_content-background\"><div class=\"circle is-header\"></div></div></div><div class=\"service-type_breadcrumb-component\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large full-bleed-18\"><div class=\"padding-section-xsmall full-bleed-20\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_component full-bleed-21\"><div data-wf--breadcrumb-original--variant=\"aligned-right\" class=\"breadcrumb_component w-variant-5112baff-e12b-04f8-68dc-4d6a7dc9da49\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/for-individuals\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">For individuals</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_current-page\">Real Estate Litigation</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><section element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"section_service-link\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"service-link_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid service-link_content\"><div class=\"service-link_content-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h2\">Services</h2></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">If you’re involved in a real estate dispute, early advice makes all the difference. Talk to us and let’s find a practical way forward.</p><div class=\"margin