iv class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was impressed by the team at Black Solicitors LLP. Every member of staff I dealt with was pleasant and professional, demonstrating a clear commitment to helping me rather than just driving up costs.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">My first time using Moonstone, I&#x27;ve used a few solicitors over time, working with team at Moonstone has been effortless and efficient, I would be happy to recommend and use again.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">It’s clear that client care and hospitality are taken seriously here. I would highly recommend Moonstone to anyone looking for a professional, welcoming and experienced legal firm.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very impressed with their experience from start to finish. The legal team were exceptionally friendly, welcoming, and professional throughout. The security staff were particularly polite and approachable, making visitors feel comfortable as soon as they arrived. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">The Real Estate Litigation team at Moonstone are in my opinion second to none. I recommend Moonstone to all my clients because I am confident they will deliver an excellent service with fantastic customer care.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Litigation Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">The team at Moonstone are in my opinion second to none. I recommend Moonstone to all my clients because I am confident they will deliver an excellent service with fantastic customer care.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Litigation Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Extensive knowledge of their area of expertise, particularly from LUgandae Maidens and Paul Sagar. Their experience in the specialised area of the Electronic Communications Code and approach to problem solving combined are particularly valuable.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Litigation Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">The team is positive and engaging and want to go above and beyond to get a great result and to achieve client&#x27;s objective.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Litigation Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">The team always go above and beyond for every client. They have several members dealing with both transactional and litigation matters. Everyone always responds in a timely manner which shows they have very good resource management. I recommend them to every client as I am so happy with their work.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Litigation Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Excellent knowledge of the particularly complex and evolving area of law that is the telecommunications market, particularly with regards to the litigation aspect. The team at Moonstone has a solid understanding of the legislation governing this market and will always offer sound and reasoned professional advice.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div c